thread.title: Shenzhen Sed Industry Revises Acquisition Plan, To Buy 51 Pct Stake In Shenzhen Electronic Equipment Firm

author: Reuters Editorial
title: Shenzhen Sed Industry Revises Acquisition Plan, To Buy 51 Pct Stake In Shenzhen Electronic Equipment Firm

organizations.name: reuters) - shenzhen sed industry co ltd

text:
Feb 13 (Reuters) - Shenzhen Sed Industry Co Ltd:
* SAYS IT PLANS TO BUY 51 PERCENT STAKE IN SHENZHEN ELECTRONIC EQUIPMENT FIRM FOR 269.0 MILLION YUAN ($42.41 million) BY CASH, DITCHING ORIGINAL PLAN TO BUY ENTIRE COMPANY Source text in Chinese: bit.ly/2BUAB6l Further company coverage: ($1 = 6.3431 Chinese yuan renminbi) (Reporting by Hong Kong newsroom)
